            <title>Google Bard 改名 Gemini   推出全新付費版服務</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/09/google-rebrands-bard-to-gemini/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=google-rebrands-bard-to-gemini</link>
